Class ServiceData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.simplity.service.ServiceData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ServiceData
extends Object
implements Serializable
    data carrier between client tier and service tier. we have few known fields that are defined as attributes. rest are carried in a generic map
